WEBVTT

00:00.835 --> 00:01.467
<i> [narrator] Previously</i>
<i>  on Queen Sugar.</i>

00:01.469 --> 00:02.835
I have a friend.

00:02.837 --> 00:06.705
Something has come up
in the friendship,
it's intimacy.

00:06.707 --> 00:08.440
I don't think
I can marry you.

00:08.442 --> 00:11.043
I'm a patient man.
I'm not going anywhere.

00:11.045 --> 00:13.879
I'd like as much love
surrounding this baby
as possible.

00:13.881 --> 00:15.681
I got an extra room.

00:15.683 --> 00:17.850
I can help you with the baby
if you need it.

00:17.852 --> 00:21.787
That cemetery you mentioned
being registered
as a historical site.

00:21.789 --> 00:23.922
Can we do something like that
with our land?

00:23.924 --> 00:24.790
Ideas for a co-op.

00:24.792 --> 00:26.925
If we put our money together,

00:26.927 --> 00:29.428
maybe we could get us
some control and some power.

00:34.835 --> 00:36.001
All right.

00:36.003 --> 00:38.170
You got everything you need?

00:38.172 --> 00:40.072
I think so.

00:40.074 --> 00:43.108
If not, I'll make do.

00:43.477 --> 00:45.177
I'll get it done.

00:46.747 --> 00:47.846
All right.

00:47.848 --> 00:52.251
Um, food, sandwiches,
snacks, coffee.

00:52.253 --> 00:53.986
Babe, we shouldn't take
too long.

00:53.988 --> 00:55.454
Okay.

00:55.456 --> 00:56.955
I ain't got no time to waste.

00:56.957 --> 00:59.858
You do what you gotta do,

00:59.860 --> 01:01.427
but you come home.

01:01.429 --> 01:03.062
I always do.

01:12.173 --> 01:13.906
I love you.

01:13.908 --> 01:15.307
I love you back.

01:18.012 --> 01:19.978
You do what you gotta do.

